</dl>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20060619031752/http://www.sringerisharadapeetham.org/html/History/guruparampara.html" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20060619031752/http://www.sringerisharadapeetham.org/html/History/guruparampara.html" rel="nofollow">"Guru Parampara of Sringeri Sharada Peetham"</a>. Archived from <a href="http://www.sringerisharadapeetham.org/html/History/guruparampara.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sringerisharadapeetham.org/html/History/guruparampara.html" rel="nofollow">the original</a> on 2006-06-19<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20060619031752/http://www.sringerisharadapeetham.org/html/History/guruparampara.html" class="external free" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20060619031752/http://www.sringerisharadapeetham.org/html/History/guruparampara.html" rel="nofollow">http://web.archive.org/web/20060619031752/http://www.sringerisharadapeetham.org/html/History/guruparampara.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Guru+Parampara+of+Sringeri+Sharada+Peetham&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20060619031752%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.sringerisharadapeetham.org%2Fhtml%2FHistory%2Fguruparampara.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Adi_Shankara"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
