<li><a href="http://www.advaita-vedanta.org/avhp/dating-Sankara.html" class="external text" title="http://www.advaita-vedanta.org/avhp/dating-Sankara.html" rel="nofollow">Sankara's date supporting the 788–820 CE date</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.easterntradition.org/original%20sankaracarya.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.easterntradition.org/original%20sankaracarya.pdf" rel="nofollow">Material supporting the 509–477 BCE dates</a> (PDF)</li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dt>Life and teachings</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.advaita-vedanta.org/avhp/sankara-life.html" class="external text" title="http://www.advaita-vedanta.org/avhp/sankara-life.html" rel="nofollow">Brief life history of Adi Shankara with informative additional links</a></li>
<li><a href="http://users.ox.ac.uk/~worc0337/authors/shankara.html" class="external text" title="http://users.ox.ac.uk/~worc0337/authors/shankara.html" rel="nofollow">Adi Śańkara</a>—short introduction to his life &amp; philosophy (by <a href="/w/index.php?title=Peter_J._King&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Peter J. King (page does not exist)">Peter J. King</a>)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.dlshq.org/saints/sankara.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.dlshq.org/saints/sankara.htm" rel="nofollow">Biography of Shankara</a> by <a href="/wiki/Swami_Sivananda" title="Swami Sivananda">Swami Sivananda</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.kamakoti.org/miscl/adi.html" class="external text" title="http://www.kamakoti.org/miscl/adi.html" rel="nofollow">Another biography of Sankara</a> from <a href="http://www.kamakoti.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.kamakoti.org/" rel="nofollow">kamakoti.org</a></li>
</ul>
